1
00:00:10,050 --> 00:00:12,420
You said love is a figment of imagination.

2
00:00:13,250 --> 00:00:14,500
I'm an imaginative guy.

3
00:00:15,040 --> 00:00:18,010
Just while you’re on this island,
you can try by buying me.

4
00:00:18,170 --> 00:00:19,650
You want me to buy love?

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:22,980
I've been thinking about the scandal
and need your help.

6
00:00:23,070 --> 00:00:24,420
How can someone like me help you?

7
00:00:24,660 --> 00:00:25,690
Will you be my girlfriend?

8
00:00:27,030 --> 00:00:28,360
I'm leaving the day after tomorrow.

9
00:00:28,750 --> 00:00:30,000
Can you not go back to Bangkok?

10
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:31,770
I promise.

11
00:00:33,150 --> 00:00:34,600
I'll do anything you say.

12
00:00:35,410 --> 00:00:36,260
Please stay with me.

13
00:00:54,210 --> 00:00:54,780
Nong Mut!

14
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:56,080
Nong Mut, Nong Mut, Nong Mut.

15
00:00:56,540 --> 00:00:57,830
Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.

16
00:00:59,050 --> 00:01:01,120
Your handsome guest’s checking out today?

17
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:02,460
How did you know?

18
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:05,459
Well, I checked the records.

19
00:01:06,070 --> 00:01:08,130
He was only booked until last night.

20
00:01:09,500 --> 00:01:11,020
Yeah, you got it right.

21
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,480
What a pity.

22
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:18,080
Because he’s a big tipper.

23
00:01:18,260 --> 00:01:20,350
Wait, what if the girls
at the bar find out?

24
00:01:20,610 --> 00:01:21,730
They’ll freak the hell out!

25
00:01:21,750 --> 00:01:24,700
They were fighting like
cats in heat to seduce him.

26
00:01:27,490 --> 00:01:28,420
What else can we do?

27
00:01:29,330 --> 00:01:30,550
He's got a home to go back to.

28
00:01:31,330 --> 00:01:32,920
You want him to stay
 and keep tipping forever?

29
00:01:35,450 --> 00:01:36,950
I was only asking.

30
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:38,710
And I was only answering.

31
