Look there.
Just go back to work.

32
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,450
Dear guest!

33
00:01:44,770 --> 00:01:46,810
Hello, please have a seat.

34
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:48,090
Are you here to check out?

35
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:50,259
Don’t forget the tip box, my dear guest.

36
00:01:51,750 --> 00:01:52,970
Just a moment, please.

37
00:02:21,270 --> 00:02:22,660
Every meeting...

38
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:26,510
