That’s not what I meant.

45
00:04:59,130 --> 00:05:00,230
I’m talking about this.

46
00:05:01,580 --> 00:05:02,040
This.

47
00:05:02,700 --> 00:05:03,600
This pickup.

48
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:06,450
Didn’t you say you didn’t own one?

49
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:09,050
When did I ever say that?

50
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:10,080
But…

51
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,730
You picked me up in a cargo tricycle.

52
00:05:12,970 --> 00:05:14,510
Took me around on a motorcycle.

53
00:05:14,810 --> 00:05:16,980
I never saw this goddamn pickup even once.

54
00:05:20,070 --> 00:05:22,480
And have I ever told you
I don’t own a pickup?

55
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:25,950
I use it to tow the boat.

56
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,660
Are you a boat that needs to be towed?

57
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:38,440
Calm down.

58
00:05:39,930 --> 00:05:41,650
Let’s not say goodbye while being upset.

59
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:50,820
You’re not that mean, are you?

60
00:07:20,290 --> 00:07:23,270
I’m sorry I couldn’t keep my promise.

61
00:07:24,610 --> 00:07:25,390
I understand.

62
00:07:26,030 --> 00:07:26,730
It’s alright.

63
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:28,790
I was there too...

64
00:07:29,660 --> 00:07:32,140
