Spanish translations, right?

86
00:08:47,370 --> 00:08:50,760
And they want to discuss Vietnam's
interest in a web series adaptation too.

87
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,650
You must attend, P’ Rak.

88
00:08:53,020 --> 00:08:55,830
I’m begging you.
Please, please, please.

89
00:08:56,410 --> 00:08:57,030
Please.

90
00:08:57,230 --> 00:08:58,170
