105
00:10:11,330 --> 00:10:12,290
You were forced to come here.

106
00:10:14,210 --> 00:10:15,910
I still remember the first day I met you.

107
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:20,870
You raised your chin like this too.

108
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:23,600
Don’t make it into a habit.

109
00:10:24,820 --> 00:10:25,650
You’ll get a stiff neck.

110
00:10:26,930 --> 00:10:27,520
I’m worried about you.

111
00:10:30,780 --> 00:10:31,820
Don’t worry about me.

112
00:10:32,300 --> 00:10:33,120
