113
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,440
And…

114
00:10:38,980 --> 00:10:39,990
Remember to eat breakfast.

115
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,260
Or you’ll get gastritis.

116
00:10:44,100 --> 00:10:44,800
