P’ Rak.

180
00:16:44,650 --> 00:16:45,030
Mook.

181
00:16:46,530 --> 00:16:47,270
This is Mahasamut.

182
00:16:48,070 --> 00:16:48,790
Get acquainted.

183
00:16:49,300 --> 00:16:50,220
I bought him back with me.

184
00:16:52,810 --> 00:16:53,420
What?!

185
00:17:49,750 --> 00:17:51,070
What floor is your room on, Khun Tongrak?

186
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:54,770
Third floor.

187
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:01,760
What are you doing?

188
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:04,350
Going to bed.

189
00:18:04,690 --> 00:18:05,750
Khun Tongrak’s tired.

190
00:18:07,100 --> 00:18:08,650
P’ Rak’s tired, then let him go to bed.

191
00:18:08,710 --> 00:18:09,950
Why are you following him?

192
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:11,840
I’m sleeping with him, of course.

193
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:13,710
You can’t.

194
00:18:19,290 --> 00:18:19,720
No.

195
00:18:24,350 --> 00:18:26,340
You’re not allowed to enter P’ Rak’s room.

196
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:27,180
Why?

197
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:28,580
I don’t trust you.

198
00:18:30,660 --> 00:18:32,260
Mook, let him be.

199
00:18:34,510 --> 00:18:35,330
P’ Rak.

200
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:36,100
But…

201
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:38,440
But he’s a complete stranger.

202
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:40,560
