205
00:18:48,090 --> 00:18:48,910
P’ Rak!

206
00:18:49,800 --> 00:18:50,690
It’s the truth.

207
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:53,730
Because if he doesn’t get into my room…

208
00:18:56,090 --> 00:18:57,310
how else would we have sex?

209
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,290
P’ Tongrak!

210
00:19:02,230 --> 00:19:02,760
Mook.

211
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:05,960
I bought him, so I have to get
my money’s worth out of him.

212
00:19:07,490 --> 00:19:08,720
Khun Tongrak’s right.

213
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:11,700
You won’t let me into his room.

214
00:19:13,210 --> 00:19:14,280
Do you want us to do it here?

215
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:17,790
I’ve got no problems with it, though.

216
00:19:18,430 --> 00:19:21,660
You can see for yourself
whether I'm worth the money or not.

217
00:19:21,690 --> 00:19:22,600
Are you crazy?

218
00:19:26,550 --> 00:19:27,160
What are you doing?

219
00:19:30,290 --> 00:19:31,090
Alright.

220
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:33,110
It’s getting late.
You should go home.

221
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:34,230
P’ Rak.

222
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:35,680
Not yet.

223
00:19:36,120 --> 00:19:37,080
But… But…

224
00:19:37,360 --> 00:19:39,130
I'm not done talking just yet.

225
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:46,440
Or do you want to see us having sex?

226
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:49,470
P’ Rak.

227
00:19:51,290 --> 00:19:53,170
Go home now.
It’s already late.

228
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:55,320
Do you know what time it is, hmm?

229
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:01,040
If you don’t leave,
I’ll bail on the meeting.

230
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:02,150
You can’t.

231
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:03,860
You absolutely can’t.

232
00:20:04,170 --> 00:20:07,010
You can bail on anything but this meeting.

233
00:20:07,180 --> 00:20:08,890
That’s why you’ve got to leave now.

234
00:20:10,060 --> 00:20:16,060
