236
00:20:21,940 --> 00:20:22,550
But…

237
00:20:22,570 --> 00:20:23,140
No but.

238
00:20:26,710 --> 00:20:27,170
Go.

239
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:29,200
Not yet, P’ Rak.
I’m still not done talking.

240
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:30,770
