577
00:42:29,580 --> 00:42:30,980
Underwear.

578
00:42:31,570 --> 00:42:32,750
Underwear.

579
00:42:36,960 --> 00:42:37,470
Oh.

580
00:42:43,680 --> 00:42:44,440
Underwear.

581
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:45,950
Underwear.

582
00:42:47,290 --> 00:42:49,410
