585
00:42:54,990 --> 00:42:56,090
I’m free tomorrow.

586
00:42:56,450 --> 00:42:57,440
I’ll go with you.

587
00:42:58,580 --> 00:43:00,040
Okay?

588
00:43:36,990 --> 00:43:37,580
What is it?

589
00:43:40,440 --> 00:43:41,390
I’ve signed it.

590
00:43:45,330 --> 00:43:47,890
Now, I’m all yours.

591
00:43:55,270 --> 00:43:56,500
I want to talk about the deal.

592
00:44:00,190 --> 00:44:00,940
The pay’s too low?

593
00:44:02,750 --> 00:44:03,430
No.

594
00:44:04,790 --> 00:44:05,630
It’s not about money.

595
00:44:08,200 --> 00:44:09,800
If I understand correctly,
despite my lack of education…

596
00:44:11,660 --> 00:44:14,600
It’s just the deal between us.

597
00:44:15,870 --> 00:44:17,280
There won’t be anything more, right?

598
00:44:22,940 --> 00:44:24,370
