608
00:45:02,200 --> 00:45:02,990
I…

609
00:45:04,370 --> 00:45:05,270
Umm…

610
00:45:06,490 --> 00:45:07,020
Yes.

611
00:45:08,480 --> 00:45:09,030
I know.

612
00:45:10,570 --> 00:45:11,820
