615
00:45:21,540 --> 00:45:22,860
Pay me as much as you want.

616
00:45:23,630 --> 00:45:24,860
Have me do whatever you want.

617
00:45:25,540 --> 00:45:27,340
But there’s one thing
you can’t dictate on paper.

618
00:45:30,830 --> 00:45:32,040
