619
00:45:33,630 --> 00:45:35,530
before we start this new relationship.

620
00:45:42,830 --> 00:45:46,970
You can't stop me from loving you.

621
00:45:51,190 --> 00:45:54,350
But I’ll never fall in love with you.

622
00:45:56,030 --> 00:45:56,470
Yes.

623
00:45:57,660 --> 00:45:58,220
I know.

624
00:46:01,150 --> 00:46:02,580
