627
00:46:21,420 --> 00:46:22,600
I figure kissing is allowed.

628
00:46:23,870 --> 00:46:25,160
The agreement doesn't forbid it.

629
00:46:27,230 --> 00:46:28,710
But you can’t do things I don’t like.

630
00:46:32,220 --> 00:46:33,180
And did you like it?

631
00:46:38,490 --> 00:46:40,010
Feel free to request my service any time.

632
00:46:42,320 --> 00:46:43,480
I'll do my best.

633
00:46:52,210 --> 00:46:53,050
If you have time…

634
00:46:54,030 --> 00:46:55,780
Think about what I said.

635
00:46:57,410 --> 00:46:58,440
I refuse.

636
00:47:07,760 --> 00:47:09,010
You can’t force me.

637
00:47:27,970 --> 00:47:29,190
What’s this love nonsense!

638
00:47:41,030 --> 00:47:43,240
Actually, you didn’t have to come with me.

639
00:47:43,570 --> 00:47:45,470
I can buy… on my own.

640
00:47:46,670 --> 00:47:47,840
I didn’t come because of you.

641
00:47:48,570 --> 00:47:49,260
I was just bored.

642
00:47:51,220 --> 00:47:52,540
Then why aren’t you resting?

643
00:47:53,030 --> 00:47:55,090
Didn’t you say you were tired from filming?

644
00:47:56,550 --> 00:47:57,940
