654
00:48:33,780 --> 00:48:34,300
P’ Vie.

655
00:48:35,050 --> 00:48:37,730
Do you think P’ Rak will
fall into that guy’s trap?

656
00:48:39,110 --> 00:48:40,770
Can’t say about the trap.

657
00:48:41,350 --> 00:48:42,620
But fall in love, maybe.

658
00:48:44,660 --> 00:48:46,380
P’ Vie.

659
00:48:46,590 --> 00:48:48,380
Be serious.

660
00:48:48,410 --> 00:48:50,820
When I finally get serious,
you won’t believe me.

661
00:48:52,270 --> 00:48:54,130
There, there, don’t pout.

662
00:48:54,860 --> 00:48:56,340
Come on, let’s go shopping.

663
00:49:01,190 --> 00:49:04,920
♪ The more my heart flutters,
the closer you get ♪

664
00:49:05,060 --> 00:49:07,630
♪ Always making moves on me ♪

665
00:49:08,890 --> 00:49:12,690
♪ My mind races like crazy
when I’m around you ♪

666
00:49:12,750 --> 00:49:15,900
♪ Please don’t play games with me ♪

667
00:49:16,190 --> 00:49:17,960
♪ The more I see you… ♪

668
00:49:17,980 --> 00:49:19,060
You’re gonna buy that one?

669
00:49:19,990 --> 00:49:21,270
Yeah. Why?

670
00:49:21,900 --> 00:49:23,450
I always buy this style for P’ Rak.

671
00:49:24,800 --> 00:49:26,470
And who are you shopping for today?

672
00:49:27,100 --> 00:49:27,810
You’re right.

673
00:49:31,620 --> 00:49:32,410
Come here.

674
00:49:32,600 --> 00:49:34,570
♪ Oh, there you go again ♪

675
00:49:34,590 --> 00:49:37,760
♪ Why wouldn’t you listen to me? ♪

676
00:49:37,780 --> 00:49:39,510
♪ Do you have a thing for me? ♪

677
00:49:39,540 --> 00:49:41,880
