678
00:49:42,210 --> 00:49:43,220
P’ Vie!

679
00:49:44,550 --> 00:49:45,700
P’ Vie.

680
00:49:46,010 --> 00:49:47,160
Put it down.

681
00:49:49,880 --> 00:49:51,160
Why are you embarrassed?

682
00:49:51,180 --> 00:49:52,980
We have to buy it anyway.

683
00:49:53,270 --> 00:49:54,210
What style do you want?

684
00:49:54,510 --> 00:49:56,650
Briefs, trunks, or something else?

685
00:49:58,090 --> 00:49:59,560
You’re a celebrity.

686
00:49:59,810 --> 00:50:02,840
What would people say
if they saw you like this?

687
00:50:03,520 --> 00:50:07,440
They’d say I’m so into my new guy
that I’m buying him underwear.

688
00:50:09,070 --> 00:50:10,530
Stop it.

689
00:50:13,920 --> 00:50:14,480
Come on.

690
00:50:15,240 --> 00:50:16,530
- Hm?
- Let’s go that way.

691
00:50:17,020 --> 00:50:19,610
