wear the clothes you pick out.

693
00:50:24,400 --> 00:50:25,110
Huh?

694
00:50:34,580 --> 00:50:36,040
- Here you are.
- Oh, thank you.

695
00:50:36,070 --> 00:50:37,130
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

696
00:50:54,470 --> 00:50:55,260
Excuse me.

697
00:50:55,720 --> 00:50:59,150
Could you tell me what
