701
00:51:05,450 --> 00:51:06,520
Oh, I just...

702
00:51:07,350 --> 00:51:09,230
I want to know which ones they bought.

703
00:51:09,320 --> 00:51:11,500
That was Khun Vivie, Veerapapha, right?

704
00:51:11,920 --> 00:51:13,470
Can you show me what she bought?

705
00:51:13,600 --> 00:51:14,680
Certainly. This way, please.

706
00:52:32,840 --> 00:52:34,210
