736
00:54:40,080 --> 00:54:40,860
Is it good?

737
00:54:44,640 --> 00:54:45,020
Well...

738
00:54:46,020 --> 00:54:46,900
It's alright.

739
00:55:18,290 --> 00:55:19,070
This isn’t a date.

740
00:55:19,170 --> 00:55:21,100
I read one of your novels last night.

741
00:55:21,310 --> 00:55:26,040
The ML took the MC out for lunch
and shopping and told him it’s a date.

742
00:55:26,070 --> 00:55:27,990
Or do you have to kiss to call it a date?

743
00:55:28,070 --> 00:55:29,180
I think I’d better get up.

744
00:55:31,140 --> 00:55:33,180
